snippet.title: Zelda 64 - F3 2023 Trailer
snippet.description:
F3 2023 teaser trailer for "Zelda 64", a beta-style mod for Ocarina of Time.

F3 Presentation: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Up6ocnxhQC8

Didn't see it on YouTube so figured I'd upload it.

The creator decided to stay anonymous according to @KazeN64 so I don't have any further info on this yet.  If they speak up or decide to post their own trailer, I'll be unlisting this one.

P.S.: Not a full game, but you can get a beta showcase with the sw97 release here: https://github.com/z64proto/sw97
